    $p() = B_1 * pow($x(), $a()-1) * pow(1-$x(), $b()-1);
  }
  else {
    barf("x out of range [0,1]");
  }
}

  ',
  Doc      => '

=for ref

probability density function for beta distribution. x defined on [0,1].

=cut

  ',

